nt/uploads/2025/01/Garth-hudson-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Garth-hudson-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Garth-hudson-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-band">The Band</a>联合创始人兼最后一位成员 Garth Hudson 去世，享年 87 岁。</p><p>这位以其独特的风琴和萨克斯管作品而闻名的加拿大多乐器演奏家于今天（1 月 21 日）在纽约州北部的十布罗克康复和护理中心去世。</p><p>据他的遗产执行人称（据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2025/jan/21/garth-hudson-founder-member-of-the-band-and-bob-dylan-collaborator-dies-aged-87" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报</em></a>》），哈德森在他居住的疗养院的睡梦中平静地去世。目前还没有透露死亡原因。在哈德森的老朋友兼同事简·豪斯特向<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/garth-hudson-the-band-dead-1234804659/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em></a>分享的一份声明中，他证实了哈德森的死亡，并表示哈德森“平静地去世”，并补充说“昨天是音乐和牵手的一天”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFGDNTcNH1v/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="5