-Clarke-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Self-Esteem.-Credit-Scarlett-Carlos-Clarke-1-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Self-Esteem.-Credit-Scarlett-Carlos-Clarke-1-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Self-Esteem.-Credit-Scarlett-Carlos-Clarke-1-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Self-Esteem.-Credit-Scarlett-Carlos-Clarke-1-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Self-Esteem.-Credit-Scarlett-Carlos-Clarke-1-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/self-esteem">Self Esteem</a>宣布推出一张名为“A Complicated Woman”的新专辑，并于今天分享第一首歌曲“Focus Is Power”。</p><p>这位歌手的真名是丽贝卡·露西·泰勒 (Rebecca Lucy Taylor)，<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFGQ5K_t2-0/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">今天在社交媒体</a>上宣布了歌曲《复杂的女人》，该歌曲将于 4 月 25 日通过 Polydor 发行。</p><p>随着专辑的消息，她分享了她的新单曲“Focus Is Power”，这是一首令人起鸡皮疙瘩的民谣，主要由女性声音组成，讲述了自信和决心。</p><p> <em>“你看，这不取决于我，但现在可以了/但现在我清楚地看到每一年的过去/我应该在这里......”</em>歌词是这样的。<a href="https://selfesteem.lnk.to/FocusisPower" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请听</a>下面的“专注就是力量”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="自尊 - 专注就是力量（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DgVqgud0L1c?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>据一份新闻稿称，《复杂的女人》旨在重新掌控自己的生活，同时揭露女性应该承担的过多和额外的劳动。</p><p> Self Esteem 的新专辑将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/moonchild-sanelly">Moonchild Sanelly</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nadine-shah">Nadine Shah</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/life-without-buildings">Life Without Buildings</a>的 Sue Tompkins 出演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFGQ